	<section>
	    <title>Install dictionaries</title>

	    <ul>
		<li>Open a terminal</li>
		<li>Download the tarball: <code>wget http://divvun.no/static_files/hunspell-se.tar.gz</code></li>
		<li>Unpack the tarball: <code>tar zxvf hunspell-se.tar.gz</code> </li>
		<li>Go in to the hunspell-se-&lt;version&gt; directory: <code>cd hunspell-se-&lt;version&gt;</code></li>
		<li>Install the dictionaries: <code>sudo make install</code></li>
	    </ul>
